==== China ====
* The State of Wu is annexed by the State of Yue.

==== Japan ====
* The Hikawa Shrine is established in Saitama, Saitama.
&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;

== Births ==

== Deaths ==
* King Fuchai of Wu, the last king of Wu in Zhou dynasty, China

